Name: ID-EGO
About the game: ID-EGO a single-player FPS game in a sci-fi setting where you are put behind enemy lines in a secret base aboard an alien spaceship. The wanna-be-overlord drone 'ID-EGO' is your backseat-driver. He will send you off into the depths of the unexplored ship and planetside out to complete missions he deem necessary. You must survive action-packed combat, solve crazy puzzles and find hidden secrets to make your way through your own adventure! ID-EGO is an old school shooter , meaning there's no hand holding you have to figure out the way yourself. Your skill decide your progress because there are no special abilities or level skipping!
